@startuml state_loan
title Loan Lifecycle — State Diagram

state Requested
state Active
state Renewed
state Overdue
state Returned
state Closed
state Rejected

[*] --> Requested : memberRequestsLoan
Requested --> Active : librarianApprovesLoan [copyAvailable] / recordIssueDate
Requested --> Rejected : librarianRejectsLoan [copyUnavailable] / notifyMember

Active --> Renewed : memberRenewsLoan [renewalCount < 2] / incrementRenewalCount; extendDueDate
Renewed --> Active : renewalConfirmed

Active --> Overdue : dueDatePassed [bookNotReturned] / calculateFine
Renewed --> Overdue : dueDatePassed [bookNotReturned] / calculateFine

Active --> Returned : memberReturnsBook / recordReturnDate
Renewed --> Returned : memberReturnsBook / recordReturnDate
Overdue --> Returned : memberReturnsBook / recordReturnDate; issueFineNotice
Returned --> Closed : fineSettledOrNone / archiveLoan
Rejected --> Closed : / archiveLoan
Closed --> [*]

@enduml
